source.name: Parks
source.description: This map is used to publish information about parks and recreation areas in a community as both points and polygons. The polygons, including some proposed parks, were originally built from parcels. The point location of the parks are derived from a subset of Facility Sites and related to a table that contains information about parks and recreation activities
